To handle HTTP POST request in express.js ,

you need to install middleware module called body-perser.


>body-parser extract the entire body portion of an incoming request of an incoming request stream and exposes

 it on req.body
 
 console.log(req.body)
 
 gives the value in object form
 
 
 property 1: req.body.v1
 
 property 2: req.body.v2


>the body-parser module parses the json,buffer,string and URL encoded data submitted using HTTP POST request  
